OL,3,CFrance becomes first European country
OL,4,Cto ban children from using social media
OL,6,FFrench politicians have passed a bill
OL,7,Fbanning children under 15 from using
OL,8,Fsocial media, becoming the first
OL,9,FEuropean country to implement such a
OL,10,Frestriction.
OL,12,FThe UK and several other European
OL,13,Fnations are considering similar
OL,14,Flegislation.
OL,16,FBoth chambers of the Parliament voted
OL,17,Fin favour of the measure, a flagship
OL,18,Finitiative of French President
OL,19,FEmmanuel Macron's second term. The
OL,20,Fbill also bans the use of mobile
OL,21,Fphones in schools.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
