OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784670507
OL,3,CFrance becomes first European country
OL,4,Cto ban children from using social media
OL,6,FSeveral families in France have sued
OL,7,FTikTok over teen suicides they say are
OL,8,Flinked to harmful content. Children's
OL,9,Fadvocates and parents applauded the
OL,10,Fvote.
OL,12,FThe legislation is one of the final
OL,13,Fmajor measures adopted under Macron's
OL,14,Fpresidency before he leaves office
OL,15,Fnext year.
OL,17,FMacron wants the law to take effect at
OL,18,Fthe start of the new school year in
OL,19,FSeptember.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
