CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784670507
OL,3,CFrance becomes first European country
OL,4,Cto ban children from using social media
OL,6,FHowever, a review to determine whether
OL,7,Fthe bill complies with the French
OL,8,FConstitution is likely to take place
OL,9,Fand could delay its implementation.
OL,11,F"France is leading the way in Europe
OL,12,Fin protecting our children and our
OL,13,Fteenagers," Macron said. "We will keep
OL,14,Fon going."
OL,16,FThe ban won't cover online
OL,17,Fencyclopaedias, or educational or
OL,18,Fscientific directories.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@KO]uD@ZOUvD@JO]
