OL,3,CFrance becomes first European country
OL,4,Cto ban children from using social media
OL,6,FThe UK is currently consulting on
OL,7,Fimplementing a similar ban that was
OL,8,Ffavoured by former Prime Minister Keir
OL,9,FStarmer.
OL,11,FAndy Burnham has said in the past he
OL,12,Ffavours the policy but has not
OL,13,Fcommented on it since he became prime
OL,14,Fminister.
OL,16,FOvernight curfews, breaks to prevent
OL,17,F"doom-scrolling", and introducing an
OL,18,FAustralian-style social media ban
OL,19,Fwhich would raise the digital age of
OL,20,Fconsent, are some of the proposals the
OL,21,Fgovernment is considering.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@PO]
