OL,3,CFrance becomes first European country
OL,4,Cto ban children from using social media
OL,6,FLawmakers from the left-wing party
OL,7,FFrance Unbowed opposed the bill,
OL,8,Farguing that its constitutionality is
OL,9,Funclear, that it would effectively end
OL,10,Fonline anonymity, and that it would be
OL,11,Fimpossible to enforce.
OL,13,FAccording to France's health watchdog,
OL,14,Fone in two teenagers spends between
OL,15,Ftwo and five hours a day on a
OL,16,Fsmartphone.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
