OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784670507
OL,3,CFrance becomes first European country
OL,4,Cto ban children from using social media
OL,6,FIn a report published in December, it
OL,7,Fsaid that some 90% of children between
OL,8,F12 and 17 use smartphones daily to
OL,9,Faccess the internet, with 58% of them
OL,10,Fusing their devices for social
OL,11,Fnetworks.
OL,13,FThe report highlighted a range of
OL,14,Fharmful effects stemming from the use
OL,15,Fof social networks, including reduced
OL,16,Fself-esteem and increased exposure to
OL,17,Fcontent associated with risky
OL,18,Fbehaviours such as self-harm, drug use
OL,19,Fand suicide.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
