OL,3,CFrance becomes first European country
OL,4,Cto ban children from using social media
OL,6,FIn 2024, Australia became the first
OL,7,Fcountry to kick kids under 16 off
OL,8,Fsocial media.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FThe law makes platforms, including
OL,16,FTikTok, Facebook, Snapchat, Reddit, X
OL,17,Fand Instagram, liable for fines if
OL,18,Fthey fail to prevent children younger
OL,19,Fthan 16 from holding accounts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
