OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784670507
OL,3,CFrance becomes first European country
OL,4,Cto ban children from using social media
OL,6,FIn Europe, Spain's prime minister
OL,7,FPedro Sanchez announced in February
OL,8,Fthat the country wants to limit social
OL,9,Fmedia access for children under 16.
OL,11,FDenmark, Greece, Austria and Norway
OL,12,Fhave all said they were considering
OL,13,Fsimilar legislation.
OL,15,FEuropean Commission President Ursula
OL,16,Fvon der Leyen earlier this month
OL,17,Fcalled for limits to be placed on
OL,18,Fchildren using social media.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
