OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784670507
OL,3,CFrance becomes first European country
OL,4,Cto ban children from using social media
OL,6,FA special EU panel looking into the
OL,7,Fissue recommended forbidding access
OL,8,Ffor those under 13 until tech
OL,9,Fcompanies can prove their platforms
OL,10,Fare safe.
OL,12,FVon der Leyen said that children under
OL,13,Fthree should have no exposure to
OL,14,Fscreens at all. She noted infinite
OL,15,Fscrolling as one of the "addictive"
OL,16,Ftraits that tech companies must
OL,17,Faddress.
